<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8">
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1,maximum-scale=1,user-scalable=no">
    	<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">
    	<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="black">
		<title>精彩瞬间-查看更多</title>
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/api.css" />
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/commonWindow.css" />
		<style type="text/css">
			html,body{
				width: 100%;
				height: 100%;
				min-width: 320px;
				background-color: #f8f8f8;
			}
			#main{
				margin-bottom: 60px;
				background-color: #fff;
			}
			.wonderfulList>li{
				padding:0 20px;
				padding-top: 20px;
				border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
			}
			.wonderfulList>li:nth-last-of-type(1){
				border-bottom: 0;
			}
			.wonderfulList>li .tp_user{
				overflow: hidden;
				padding-bottom: 10px;
			}
			.wonderfulList>li .tp_user .userPic{
				width: 36px;
				height: 36px;
				border-radius: 50%;
				float: left;
				margin-right: 8px;
			}
			.wonderfulList>li .tp_user .userPic img{
				width: 100%;
				height: 100%;
				border-radius: 50%;
			}
			.wonderfulList>li .tp_user .userInfo{
				font-size: 14px;
				color: #666666;
				letter-spacing: 0.29px;
			}
			.wonderfulList>li .tp_user .userInfo .username{
				padding-top: 8px;
				line-height: 20px;
				position: relative;
			}
			.wonderfulList>li .tp_user .userInfo .username em{
				line-height: 10px;
				font-size: 10px;
				color: #909090;
				letter-spacing: 0.21px;
				position: absolute;
				right: 0;
				top: 14px;
			}
			.ct_content p{
				font-size: 15px;
				color: #000000;
				letter-spacing: 0.5px;
				line-height: 19px;
			}
			.ct_content ul{				
				padding-top: 10px;
				width: 100%;
				overflow: hidden;
				
			}
			.ct_content ul li{
				width: 100%;
				height: 190px;
				overflow: hidden;
			}
			.ct_content ul li.ltpic{
				float: left;
				width: 48.95%;
				height: 190px;
				
			}
			.ct_content ul li.rtpic{
				float: right;
				width: 49.25%;
				height: 190px;
				
			}
			.ct_content ul li.ltpic img{
				width: 100%;
				height: 100%;
				border-radius: 15px 0 0 15px;
			}
			.ct_content ul li.rtpic img:nth-of-type(1){
				float: right;
				width: 100%;
				height: 92px;
				border-radius: 0 15px 0 0;
				margin-bottom: 6px;
			}
			.ct_content ul li.rtpic img:nth-of-type(2){
				float: right;
				width: 100%;
				height: 92px;
				border-radius: 0 0 15px 0;
				margin-bottom: 6px;
			}
			.bt_moreheat{
				padding-top: 10px;
				overflow: hidden;
				padding-bottom: 13px;
			}
			.bt_moreheat .lt_label{
				float: left;
			}
			.bt_moreheat .lt_label em{
				color: #9d9d9d;
				font-size: 12px;
				border: 1px solid #9d9d9d;
				border-radius: 5px;
				line-height: 18px;
				box-sizing: border-box;
				padding: 0 6px;
				margin-right: 5px;
			}
			.bt_moreheat .rt_apcr{
				float: right;
				overflow: hidden;
				font-size: 12px;
				color: #A3A3A3;
				letter-spacing: 0.25px;
				line-height: 18px;
				float: right;
			}
			
			.rt_apcr em{
				float: left;
				padding-left: 21px;
				width: 16px;
				height: 18px;
				padding-top: 1px;
				/*background: url(../../image/dianzan2.png) no-repeat;*/
				background-repeat: no-repeat;
			}
			.rt_apcr i{
				float: left;
				margin-left: 15px;
				padding-left: 22px;
				margin-top: 1px;
				width: 17px;
				height: 18px;
				/*background: url(../../image/pinglun2.png) no-repeat;*/
				background-repeat: no-repeat;
			}
			.rt_apcr b{
				float: left;
				margin-left: 12px;
				padding-left: 15px;
				font-weight: 400;
				width: 18px;
				height: 18px;
				/*background: url(../../image/more02.png) no-repeat;*/
				background-repeat: no-repeat;
			}
			.comment_cnt{
				background: #F2F2F2;
				border-radius: 4px;
				padding: 12px;
				padding-bottom: 6px;
				margin-top: 12px;
			}
			.comment_cnt p{
				font-size: 12px;
				color: #151515;
				line-height: 17px;
				padding-bottom: 6px;
			}
			.comment_cnt em i{
				font-size: 12px;
				color: #5AC8E1;
			}
			.comment_cnt p.more_cnt{
				font-size: 12px;
				color: #5AC8E1;
				line-height: 17px;
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<div id="main" >
		    <ul class="wonderfulList">
		    	<li>
		    		<div class="tp_user">
		    			<div class="userPic"><img src="../../image/teacherAvatar.png" alt="" /></div>
		    			<div class="userInfo">
		    				<p class="username"><span>雪花</span> <em>1分钟</em></p>
		    			</div>
		    		</div>
		    		<div class="ct_content">
		    			<p>感觉好棒！</p>
		    			
		    		</div>
		    		<div class="comment_cnt">
		    			<p><em><i>淑静:&nbsp;&nbsp;</i></em>愿孩子每天开开心心，健康成长。</p>
		    			<p><em><i>雪花</i>回复<i>淑静:&nbsp;&nbsp;</i></em>孩子的开心就是我们的最大收获。</p>
		    			<p><em><i>淑静</i>回复<i>雪花:&nbsp;&nbsp;</i></em>孩子太乖未必是好事，只是在顺从抚育者的需要。</p>
		    			<p><em><i>雪花</i>回复<i>淑静:&nbsp;&nbsp;</i></em>的确是。</p>
		    		</div>
		    		<div class="bt_moreheat">
		    			
		    			<div class="rt_apcr">
		    				<em style="background-image: url(../../image/dianzan2.png);">223</em>
			    			<i style="background-image: url(../../image/pinglun2.png);">342</i>
			    			<b style="background-image: url(../../image/more02.png);"></b>
		    			</div>
		    		</div>
		    	</li>
		    </ul>
		</div>
	</body>
	<script type="text/javascript" src="../../script/api.js"></script>
	<script type="text/javascript" src="../../script/util.js"></script>
	<script type="text/javascript" src="../../script/kv.js"></script>
	<script type="text/javascript" src="../../script/apiCloud.js"></script>
	<script type="text/javascript" src="../../script/public.js"></script>
	<script type="text/javascript" src="../../script/template-native.js"></script>
	<script type="text/javascript" src="../../script/data.js"></script>
	<script>
		apiready = function () {
			
		};
		
		
	
	</script>
</html>
